---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | FNE"
  description="Terms of service for the Figma Naming Enforcer (FNE) CLI tool and Figma plugin."
>
  <Header />
  <main id="main-content">
    <section class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-primary-900">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-primary-500">Effective Date: March 26, 2026</p>
        <div class="prose prose-primary mt-8 max-w-none">
          <h2>1. License</h2>
          <p>FNE is distributed under the MIT License.</p>

          <h2>2. Disclaimer</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Rename suggestions are AI-generated and should be reviewed before applying.</li>
            <li>The plugin includes rollback functionality, but you should verify renamed layers.</li>
            <li>Halisonworks AS is not liable for changes made to your Figma files.</li>
            <li>The tool is provided "as is" without warranty.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>3. API Costs</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Anthropic API costs for LLM analysis are your responsibility.</li>
            <li>Figma API access is subject to Figma's terms and rate limits.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>4. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>Norwegian law. Oslo courts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
